<h1 class="hed">
    <a href="/photo/2015/04/photos-of-the-week-328-43/389631/">
        Photos of the Week: 3/28-4/3
    </a>
</h1>
<p class="dek"><span>This week we have images of a </span><span>fuel tank fire in Sao Paulo, Brazil, a massive live-in sculpture of a woman in Tijuana, Mexico, the recapturing of Tikrit, Iraq, from ISIS fighters, Holy Week in Spain, election celebrations in Nigeria, Typhoon Maysak seen from orbit, a wooden car in India, flooding in Chile, the troubled tunnel-boring machine Bertha in Seattle, and much more.</span></p>

            </li>
            
